    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"110087\">Scott Morrison</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/Updating.20leanproject/near/204353775\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>What does <code>leanproject --version</code> say?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Just as I said, </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">leanproject</span> <span class=\"c1\">--version</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Usage</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">leanproject</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">OPTIONS</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"n\">COMMAND</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">ARGS</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"bp\">...</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Try</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;leanproject -h&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">for</span> <span class=\"kn\">help</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">no</span> <span class=\"n\">such</span> <span class=\"n\">option</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"c1\">--version</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 204354076,
        "sender_full_name": "Dan Stanescu",
        "timestamp": 1595170314
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"110050\">Sebastien Gouezel</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/Updating.20leanproject/near/204353777\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Does <code>pip install --upgrade mathlibtools</code> work?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Yes! This gives me version <code>0.0.9</code>. Thank you!</p>",
